INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("67","1","2016-01-25 16:09:22","2016-01-25 16:09:22","Is your organization considering going down the path for Magnet designation or re-designation? Are you faced with a lot of questions and considerations about where to start? How to  progress through your journey to nursing excellence?\r\n\r\nPartnering with HealthLinx alleviates these concerns and ensures you achieve your goals and accomplish the Magnet designation your organization covets. By working with the leader in the industry, HealthLinx will take your organization through all phases of the ANCC Magnet Recognition Program<sup>®</sup> process.\r\n\r\nWe have a 100% client success rate with designation and re-designation, and nearly 25% of ALL currently designated Magnet hospitals partnered with HealthLinx to successfully achieve designation. Around 50% of hospitals that apply on their own and do not use consulting services fail to reach Magnet status on the first try. Partner with HealthLinx to remove any doubt, inspire confidence and guarantee you reach the Magnet designation desired.\r\n\r\nHealthLinx provides a comprehensive organizational assessment of your nursing operations with a detailed project plan. This includes customized solutions to implement the project plan to achieve organizational goals and outcomes.\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Services</strong>\r\n• Evaluation of essential resources to support operational excellence\r\n• Assessment of performance outcomes and goals crucial to overall performance and financial impact\r\n• Diagnosis of problem areas with recommendations for improvements\r\n• Providing a unique view of unit-level summary outcomes\r\n• Continuity Model – we work with you from designation to designation\r\n• Report of Recommendations &amp; Project Plan\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Benefits</strong>\r\n• A proven track record that guarantees successfully reaching Magnet designation - 100% client success rate\r\n• Best-practice management of the process from start to finish and beyond– you’re never on your own at any step\r\n• An independent, third-party view of your current situation by a nursing expert and ability to objectively identify areas to improve and recommend an action plan\r\n• Comfort and stability in working with a team partnered with nearly a quarter of ALL designated Magnet hospitals throughout the country\r\n• We know your situation, no matter the challenges, by providing you with a dedicated team that’s been in hundreds of hospitals\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Team</strong>\r\n• Our Nursing Excellence team consists of Master’s and Doctorally prepared, experienced nurse leaders\r\n• MPD’s through CNO’s driving operational nursing excellence at community-based hospitals up to large academic centers\r\n• Versatile IT department accomplished in publishing\r\n• PHD-prepared, experienced copy editor dedicated solely to the copy editing work and not pulled in other areas\r\n• Relate to organizations and leaders from experience, maintain currency with professional developments, and the evolution of healthcare\r\n\r\nInterested in learning more about our Magnet services? Check out the following resources:\r\n• Webinars\r\n• Case Studies\r\n• Whitepapers\r\n• Blogs\r\n\r\n[contentblock id=2 img=gcb.png]","Magnet","","publish","closed","closed","","magnet","","","2016-02-26 14:46:23","2016-02-26 14:46:23","","19","http://beta.healthlinx.com/?page_id=67","1","page","","0");
