INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("75","1","2016-01-25 16:53:55","2016-01-25 16:53:55","<strong>Opportunities with Healthcare Organizations</strong>\r\nHealthLinx builds long-term relationships with hospitals and leaders nationwide to provide leadership solutions. With our Transitional and Permanent Leadership programs, we are constantly working to place leaders in the perfect position for their careers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Permanent Leadership</strong>\r\nOur Permanent Leadership program is a nationwide network of both seasoned and emerging leaders who partner with HealthLinx to align their interests and accomplishments with the needs of our clients:\r\n\r\nOur team of both clinical and operational experts will advocate on your behalf and provide:\r\n• Firsthand knowledge on the culture and the needs/goals of the hospital/department\r\n• Support and immediate feedback throughout the entire process\r\n• Resume writing/assistance\r\n• Compensation Negotiation\r\n• Interview Coaching/Preparation\r\n• Relocation and On-boarding assistance\r\n\r\n<strong>Transitional Leadership</strong>\r\nOur Transitional Leadership program consists of a network of accomplished leaders who we partner with to provide immediate short-term leadership creating long-lasting solutions for our clients.\r\n\r\nOur Transitional Leaders enjoy the benefits of:\r\n• Opportunity to share your expertise and improve patient care with hospitals nationwide\r\n• Continuous Clinical and Operational support\r\n• Competitive compensation, with routine travel and paid expenses\r\n• Short term consulting engagements averaging 4-6 months in length\r\n• Selectivity on engagement location and project\r\n\r\n<strong>Career Opportunities</strong>\r\nTo search available Leadership Career Opportunities, please login below or call one of our search consultants. (Note: not all opportunities are listed on our site.)\r\n\r\nTo learn about our available Transitional and Permanent Leadership opportunities, please contact one of our